name: NooShekhinah-VR
description:
Image from the Cybersex gallery of the virtual museum of the NooMuseum by Yann Minh.
The symbol represented by the two hands is the female part of God, as described by Leonard Nimoy, the actor who plays Spok in Star Trek, when he describes the genesis of the Vulcan encounter sign.

Janvier 2020.

http://www.noomuseum.net/


The noomuseum is free to download in Mac, PC, Linux version here: 
http://www.noomuseum.net/noopedagogie.html
